properties.headline: Winter Weather Advisory issued February 11 at 2:39PM CST until February 12 at 6:00PM CST by NWS Dodge City KS
properties.description:
...Wintry precipitation expected after midnight into Wednesday in
South Central Kansas...

* WHAT...Wet snow expected. Total snow accumulations of up to
one to two inches.

* WHERE...Pratt and Barber Counties.

* WHEN...From midnight tonight to 6 PM CST Wednesday.

* IMPACTS...Plan on slippery road conditions. The hazardous
conditions could impact the morning or evening commute.
properties.instruction:
Slow down and use caution while traveling.

The latest road conditions for the state you are calling from can
be obtained by calling 5 1 1.

NWSheadline: WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM MIDNIGHT TONIGHT TO 6 PM CST WEDNESDAY
